Install npm
Project needs bundler, Code must be minified, packaged and bundled. Webpack bundled.Parcel - Package bundler
Npm install parcel —registry=https://registry.npmjs.org



Package-lock.json has exact version of what package is installed
Package-lock has has of sha-512 to maintain exact same version in local and production
Each dependency has its own package.json

npx parcel index.html ( Source File )
npm - To install a package
npx - To execute a package


Browser scripts cannot have imports or exports.
Add type=module in scripts, to understand it’s not a normal browser script.


# Parcel
- Dev build
- Local server
- HMR - Hot Module Replacement
- uses File watching algorithm (C++)
- Image optimization (Images in our site)
- Minification - Minify our file for production build
- Bundling
- Compressing
- Consistent Hashing
- Code Splitting
- Differential bundling


npx parcel index.html --no-cache --https


remove "main": App.js from package.json


Production build
npx parcel build index.html --no-cache

One html
One css
One js file